BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Toronto Wellness
UID:event_313910986@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260412T031523Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T110000
SUMMARY:Vipassana Meditation & Pranayama | Clear Mind & Emotional Balance
DESCRIPTION:TORONTO WELLNESS | Yoga\, Art Therapy\, Meditation\, Chakra\n*
 *Vipassana Meditation & Pranayama \\| Clear Mind & Emotional Balance**\n\n
 Dive into a moment of inner calm and recentring. Join this online session 
 and practice with me a combination of pranayama and Vipassana meditation t
 o clear your mind and harmonize your emotions. An experience accessible to
  everyone\, in a supportive and guided space.\n\n**Why join?**\n• 🌟 *
 *Mental clarity:** Learn to observe your thoughts without judgment and rel
 ease accumulated stress.\n• 🌬️ **Vital energy:** Re-energize your b
 ody and mind with targeted breathing techniques.\n• 🌊 **Emotional bal
 ance:** Achieve a state of serenity in the face of daily challenges throug
 h better emotional management.\n• 🧘‍♂️ **Presence and grounding
 :** Enhance your ability to fully live in the present moment.\n• 🌍 **
 Accessibility:** A guided online practice\, open to everyone\, with no pri
 or experience required.\n\n**Prepare your space for an optimal experience*
 *\n• Choose a quiet place\, free from distractions.\n• Use a yoga mat 
 or meditation cushion for added comfort.\n• Keep a bottle of water nearb
 y.\n• Turn off notifications to fully immerse yourself in this moment fo
 r yourself.\n• Optional: Light a natural incense (white sage\, palo sant
 o\, patchouli\, etc.).\n\n**Session outline**\n\n1. **Introduction & Prana
 yama:** Simple breathing techniques to prepare the body and mind for medit
 ation.\n2. **Vipassana explanation & instructions:** A brief overview of V
 ipassana principles and practice guidelines.\n3. **Guided practice:** Imme
 rse yourself in a supportive and nurturing meditation experience.\n4. **Di
 scussion & Q&A:** An open space to ask questions and share your experience
 .\n\n**Practical information**\n• **Platform:** Zoom (link provided with
  the event).\n• **Access:** The waiting room opens 15 minutes before the
  start and remains accessible up to 5 minutes after the session begins. Af
 ter this time\, access will no longer be possible to preserve the quality 
 of the group experience.\n\n**Session led by Ludovic\, YE Master**\nTake t
 his time for yourself. Your journey to a peaceful mind begins here. 🌟\n
 \n**✨ Join Our Wellness Community**\nThis session is your gateway to dee
 per guidance. Continue your journey with:\n\nMore on [https://www.yogasour
 ce.org](https://www.yogasource.org)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/toronto-wellness-yoga-art-therapy-med
 itation-chakra/events/313910986/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260323T150254Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T150254Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Toronto Wellness
UID:event_313912132@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260412T031523Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T113000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T123000
SUMMARY:Chakra Healing | Rebalance Your Inner Energy
DESCRIPTION:TORONTO WELLNESS | Yoga\, Art Therapy\, Meditation\, Chakra\n
 🌿 Chakra Healing – Rebalance Your Inner Energy 🌿\n\nDive into an i
 mmersive vibrational experience to harmonize your energy and enhance your 
 emotional resilience. This 1-hour online session will guide you through po
 werful practices to realign your energy centers\, release blockages\, and 
 cultivate deep well-being.\n\n🌟 Why Join?\n✅ Dissolve energetic block
 ages that disrupt your inner balance\n✅ Increase vitality and mental cla
 rity by aligning your chakras\n✅ Experience powerful practices to deepen
  your spiritual connection\n✅ Receive energetic guidance to sustain the 
 benefits beyond the session\n\nThis experience is open to beginners and ad
 vanced practitioners alike.\n\n🧘‍♂️ Prepare Your Space:\n• Find
  a quiet place where you won’t be disturbed\n• Set up a yoga mat\, a c
 ushion\, and a glass of water\n• Use headphones or a speaker for full im
 mersion in vibrational sounds\n• Wear comfortable clothing to support mo
 vement and breathwork\n\n🗒️ Session Flow:\n1\\. Opening & Intention S
 etting – Alignment and connection\n2\\. Activation Meditation – Awaren
 ess of energy flows\n3\\. Tibetan Bowl Frequencies – Purification and ac
 tivation\n4\\. Mantras & Pranayama – Elevating vibrations and strengthen
 ing vital energy\n5\\. Sacred Chant & Integration – Vibrational closing 
 and expansion\n\n📌 Practical Information:\n🔹 Platform: Zoom (link av
 ailable in the event details)\n🔹 Timing: The waiting room opens 20 minu
 tes before the session starts and remains accessible until 10 minutes afte
 r. After this time\, entry will no longer be possible to ensure a smooth a
 nd immersive experience.\n\n💫 Guidance:\nThis session is led by Ludovic
 \, YE Master – Yoga Engineering (YE) integrates yogic sciences into its 
 approach.\n\n✨ Session Practices Overview:\n🔹 Introduction & Chakra M
 editation – Connection to your energy system\n🔹 Tibetan Bowl Vibratio
 ns – Energetic activation through sacred frequencies\n🔹 Bija Mantras 
 – Chanting primordial sounds to amplify energetic resonance\n🔹 Pranay
 ama – Breathwork techniques to awaken subtle energy\n🔹 Sacred Chantin
 g – Vibrational elevation and final integration\n\n✅ Reserve your spot
  now and embark on a transformative inner journey!\n\n**✨ Join Our Welln
 ess Community**\nThis session is your gateway to deeper guidance. Continue
  your journey with:\n\nMore on [https://www.yogasource.org](https://www.yo
 gasource.org)\n\n🌿 Activate your energy. Elevate your vibration. Let th
 e transformation unfold. 🌿
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/toronto-wellness-yoga-art-therapy-med
 itation-chakra/events/313912132/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260323T160451Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T160451Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Toronto Wellness
UID:event_313926346@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260412T031523Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260413T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260413T120000
SUMMARY:Art Therapy | My Inner Mirror | 🪞 Draw Your Inner Self
DESCRIPTION:TORONTO WELLNESS | Yoga\, Art Therapy\, Meditation\, Chakra\n
 🪞 My Inner Mirror – Inner Alchemy Workshop Through Art Therapy 🎨\n
 \nImmerse yourself in a unique and transformative workshop\, blending arti
 stic creation\, meditation\, and inner exploration. This guided introspect
 ive space will allow you to manifest your inner reality through art\, shif
 ting perceptions and strengthening your connection with your subconscious.
 \n\n🌟 Why Join?\n\n✅ Visually express your inner world and uncover it
 s hidden messages\n✅ Deepen your connection with your subconscious throu
 gh guided meditation\n✅ Use art as a tool for transformation and self-an
 alysis\n✅ Learn interpretation techniques to better understand your crea
 tions\n\nNo artistic skills required – this workshop is accessible to ev
 eryone!\n\n🧘‍♂️ Workshop Flow:\n\n1. Breathing Exercises – Ment
 al and energetic preparation for meditation\n2. Guided Meditation – Acti
 vating the subconscious and awakening intuition\n3. Mirror Drawing Creatio
 n – Representing your inner reality through art\n4. Interpretation & Exa
 mples – Understanding the symbols and messages within your artwork\n5. S
 haring & Q/A – A space for discussion and guidance\n\n📌 Required Mate
 rials:\n\n🔹 Paper: Blank sheets (A4 or A3 format\, no grid lines)\n🔹
  Artistic tools: Pencils\, brushes\, markers\, or any medium of your choic
 e\n\n⏳ Duration: 2 hours\n\n💫 Guidance:\n\nThis workshop is led by Lu
 dovic\, exploring inner alchemy through yoga and art therapy.\n\n🪞 Let 
 your true essence emerge\, observe your inner reflection\, and uncover the
  secrets your subconscious wishes to reveal.\n\n✅ Reserve your spot now 
 and embark on this transformative journey!\n\n**✨ Join Our Wellness Comm
 unity**\nMore on [https://www.yogasource.org](https://www.yogasource.org)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/toronto-wellness-yoga-art-therapy-med
 itation-chakra/events/313926346/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260324T144656Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260324T144656Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
